{"tid":178621,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(求解決)男朋友沖涼條毛巾keep住都好臭","createTime":"2017-03-29T16:01:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T08:38:35.000Z","uid":93069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"719bd73b9eebd26ba5e62230f85bdd6d70f51f3f","tid":178621,"uid":93069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:01:36.000Z","msg":"同男朋友一齊住，佢沖涼條毛巾永遠都好臭，<br />\n係好刺鼻果種臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我嗰條毛巾同佢嗰條放係附近，好正常，無味。<br />\n我已經每個星期keep住幫佢換，但佢一用咗2,3日就已經開始發臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲知道點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想根治個問題"},{"pid":"93f96e7f68c7307ee828406dd9b32a8eb79be7f8","tid":178621,"uid":71453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:02:56.000Z","msg":"買多兩條 晚晚換"},{"pid":"059c5d36ea8b0a0cbc6f045803f8bb99d0cf2ff2","tid":178621,"uid":65770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:04:10.000Z","msg":"係咪成有黑點？有就係發霉<br />\n比太陽晒下"},{"pid":"1443a59313df3a42b4069b460b6171c6cf9ab781","tid":178621,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:04:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1a47d2bae5903b8a74c0ec7a93a14f8e5dfd638","tid":178621,"uid":93069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:05:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買多兩條 晚晚換</blockquote><br />\n好似好浪費咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我諗緊會唔會係佢身上有一種細菌"},{"pid":"d735e825a07875c277d3d4f1539f56f8282d94f3","tid":178621,"uid":69275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:05:14.000Z","msg":"買條新，再洗密啲，應該有菌"},{"pid":"3fbc7cf367d6698ce7235