8621,"uid":6959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:26:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a0046fb339e3fdca72fa37aa14b284440160fec","tid":178621,"uid":75768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:31:52.000Z","msg":"換男朋友，認真<br />\n呢個人個人衛生好有問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用完要毛巾洗幾野先扭乾掛起是常識吧"},{"pid":"03ba860b1df38f91f6862266eb8def20676030d6","tid":178621,"uid":55849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:35:37.000Z","msg":"日日洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9569483e171b96a9119e39f12e94d349a246535","tid":178621,"uid":54923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:36:01.000Z","msg":"通常毛巾臭 係因為有油 佢係唔係成日就咁拎黎抹面 之後冇再洗？"},{"pid":"03818a3fdaeb0deb69d0e13a1e5dffd01b2f43f3","tid":178621,"uid":93069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:40:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常毛巾臭 係因為有油 佢係唔係成日就咁拎黎抹面 之後冇再洗？</blockquote><br />\n慘呀 佢淨係用黎抹身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b4d1c4e96348d78f5e63e7f82b97d8a80b4f2b","tid":178621,"uid":60238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:43:14.000Z","msg":"洗衫落d消毒藥水，威路士嗰隻落半蓋，洗完幾香的，唔同滴露嗰隻閪味<br />\n彩漂都得，但d衫會好硬，多多柔順劑都唔夠"},{"pid":"e072560424879be5ecdfa1d837dd19391567708c","tid":178621,"uid":41870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:46:24.000Z","msg":"你係點晾毛巾架？<br />\n我之前都有試好似你男朋友咁<br />\n後來改左晾毛巾方法，毛巾就無晒味，因為好快晾得乾就無乾<br />\n我係一條垂直晾，只有毛巾頭端輕輕用衣夾夾住個衣架個底（即係個三角形個底）<br />\nSor 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4032c9770de15ca89931247172556f7ae1d1c48d","tid":178621,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:46:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"438f7b9f3d7e9fedc9911acd08775cf4e3e34b88","tid":178621,"uid":3032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:51:44.000Z","msg":"分手"},{"pid":"63fc17bf65dc064fca40eed68c2117c79d811aac","tid":178621,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:55:21.000Z","msg":"要快d乾 就應該無乜味<br />\n可能你條仔用毛巾打j"},{"pid":"f8e441d0baed3fce86d14685896352f71208a52e","tid":178621,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:58:26.000Z","msg":"用完放係太陽曬到既地方"},{"pid":"738016d2c10f42bc1782c2687a61f043bffd2c1a","tid":178621,"uid":85409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T16:59:58.000Z","msg":"精緊係臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47284ee0be3661a984a9fe176c1b91e0e06d2555","tid":178621,"uid":1392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T17:00:04.000Z","msg":"咁咪買多幾條，一條用兩日就洗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咩人咩毛巾係沖涼房up得耐都臭啦下嘛"},{"pid":"a78f6c8c38e53905b2ff6aea62f27cd15ba57ebd","tid":178621,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T17:07:24.000Z","msg":"佢啲衫有冇味<br />\n有時男人有種好刺鼻嘅臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果唔明邊種可以試下逢賽馬日走入馬會麻甩佬堆中就會聞到"},{"pid":"0e2c9d6755ad7dd43e00c81c9cdf2dbf2e3dc249","tid":178621,"uid":66213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T17:07:40.000Z","msg":"會唔會係佢唔洗屎忽窿<br />\n之後又拎條毛巾抹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a1e60f99dbf2078cfccb4a0287cfd25f4ced38","tid":178621,"uid":93069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T17:09:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢啲衫有冇味<br />\n有時男人有種好刺鼻嘅臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor