msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>分手</blockquote><br />\n我好愛佢咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係不係只用 沐浴露無用番梘<br />\n要用番梘先有效咁除到格甩底的臭</blockquote><br />\n用滴露得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n得的話點會仲有咁多人用番梘，番梘咁不方便<br />\n信我啦，我以前都有，轉左用番梘就無事了"},{"pid":"4d4d26b1b039355c38929f06c82a6af3e80e8f66","tid":178621,"uid":57898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T17:28:49.000Z","msg":"利申：3年住hall經驗 個個仔都係咁"},{"pid":"a720aa30366e3003e4fada6be05b6099fa928723","tid":178621,"uid":1191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T17:30:10.000Z","msg":"2-3換一次，佢沖又唔乾淨，抹上身咪會有菌咪臭囉。日日換一條乾淨咪得囉懶鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad37492387965e36ff3da0b8ad60a42724c55a4","tid":178621,"uid":93069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T17:33:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2-3換一次，佢沖又唔乾淨，抹上身咪會有菌咪臭囉。日日換一條乾淨咪得囉懶鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係好浪費喎，不如叫佢用抹手紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec5f9b2a0728aed50fee05a752786192bf6ce1d","tid":178621,"uid":1191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T17:36:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>2-3換一次，佢沖又唔乾淨，抹上身咪會有菌咪臭囉。日日換一條乾淨咪得囉懶鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係好浪費喎，不如叫佢用抹手紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n換一條唔係掉左佢，係拎去洗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n浪費係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd6cbbb9a52110bdf42c3b0ff0f90d537e421cf","tid":178621,"uid":62444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T17:46:32.000Z","msg":"我啲毛巾抹一次就洗個喎... 抹幾次先洗咪up住囉..."},{"pid":"6787fd766841e7b503ce1e7b1116a2ebb1431fea","tid":178621,"uid":82078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T17:50:54.000Z","msg":"好大條嗰啲定係兩三個手掌嗰啲size"},{"pid":"054ce278e37f5049d5afbac4103827371f4f6117","tid":178621,"uid":29203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T18:18:15.000Z","msg":"我男朋友條毛巾又係咁<br />\n之前洗完過一星期左右又臭返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓上話用番梘work<br />\n我男朋友由沐浴露轉番梘之後又好似無咁臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定可能係佢兩條毛巾輪住咁用所以無咁臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有如果樓主男朋友有用個啲止汗劑<br />\n都要洗得乾淨啲<br />\n唔係陣味仲臭過你本身出汗嘅臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19909693295dfb51a1ca7e8b9b8b8cd3b6a20289","tid":178621,"uid":74728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T18:25:01.000Z","msg":"放落洗衣機洗"},{"pid":"70422ab8116eadaa664340d193bc69dd47f840c9","tid":178621,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T18:27:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢啲衫有冇味<br />\n有時男人有種好刺鼻嘅臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果唔明邊種可以試下逢賽馬日走入馬會麻甩佬堆中就會聞到</blockquote><br />\n佢有部份著得耐嘅衫會有呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁冇辦法啦係體質問題， 冇得改<br />\n以前身邊都有個咁嘅朋友， 係好惡頂㗎<br />\n因為嗰種臭味係刺鼻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都逐漸疏遠佢"},{"pid":"8f137364879fa6e4089ca02751f7a04eed1a75c9","tid":178621,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T18:38:57.000Z","msg":"check吓有無心跳"},{"pid":"f68cbba04ba207a24f79e8c3518c5f91069bd4f0","tid":178621,"uid":9412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T19:16:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢啲衫有冇味<br />\n有時男人有種好刺鼻嘅臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果唔明邊種可以試下逢賽馬日走入馬會麻甩佬堆中就會聞到</blockquote><br />\n佢有部份著得耐嘅衫會有呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁冇辦法啦係體質問題， 冇得改<br />\n以前身邊都有個咁嘅朋友， 係好惡頂㗎<br />\n因為嗰種臭味係刺鼻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都逐漸疏遠佢</blockquote><br />\n你有當佢朋友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b1201f9c5383a84129870e5456854064a3bccd","tid":178621,"uid":17408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T20:11:14.000Z","msg":"可能係你男朋友都覺得你條毛巾臭呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416bb4c3e63d98aeec3aa4c560ceaa8eee066618","tid":178621,"uid":3270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T20:35:02.000Z","msg":"所以我日日換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d82824dcbe3beb509d79da274aac4f68571567","tid":178621,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T20:38:51.000Z","msg":"米青味"},{"pid":"8dc936055afa0b9edfedcda751140124ae065f40","tid":178621,"uid":18283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T20:53:43.000Z","msg":"癡撚線 唔係應該日日換㗎咩？"},{"pid":"3cb13ce8124f27b4541cb347ede0bd137c69be85","tid":178621,"uid":35504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T22:17:03.000Z","msg":"汗味定up味？？<br />\n用衣架掛起 擺喺通爽位置會好啲"},{"pid":"d73057ee8271a77b29bdd8d38211faab2eaac645","tid":178621,"uid":88829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T22:30:09.000Z","msg":"用黎打左丁<br />\n梗臭啦"},{"pid":"46738cafa8b0e91b3cedbbeb99c4a3b24f0bbda5","tid":178621,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T23:51:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>換男朋友，認真<br />\n呢個人個人衛生好有問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用完要毛巾洗幾野先扭乾掛起是常識吧</blockquote><br />\n從來無<br />\n亦未聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用完拎掛出去曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e7c0aee88b0c5a8694e95266423b0dc98db07a6","tid":178621,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T23:53:37.000Z","msg":"有無可能佢會用風筒吹條毛巾？<br />\n之前條毛巾洗完未乾<br />\n我又要沖涼<br />\n拎風筒吹佢<br />\n第二日臭到仆街<br />\n點洗都臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"039ed5803754dd607088f9e2c5e02dc9ed2cecc0","tid":178621,"uid":36817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T23:54:31.000Z","msg":"發霉<br />\n換過條"},{"pid":"d0fb5452c623039b5390df7f3cafd413b86015ea","tid":178621,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T23:54:52.000Z","msg":"我依家條毛巾一個月唔洗唔換都唔臭"},{"pid":"6e4c5695cab4ba79bddf8fddda43b2562ecb250b","tid":178621,"uid":13505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:02:23.000Z","msg":"平時有冇噴開止汗劑？"},{"pid":"cbf62ee3ece051858c915639ebc6b03dce4e5da3","tid":178621,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:03:39.000Z","msg":"基佬毛巾係臭d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"376f6e66bf5d9878a7863b80f9d9b98ff25e6f1a","tid":178621,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:06:28.000Z","msg":"我條巾用成兩星期冇洗都唔會臭 人既問題"},{"pid":"8e2fe52225c21f2d57fd1ee9ec5b803dbb4d323e","tid":178621,"uid":31837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:18:33.000Z","msg":"買條運動用嗰啲防臭毛巾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d5f65f5aa3f3bf0f1a9374e0cb271d27748768e","tid":178621,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:20:24.000Z","msg":"用左條毛巾黎抆屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a49144eebf6af5e7efa0c74b092aad945df539","tid":178621,"uid":79485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:21:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同男朋友一齊住，佢沖涼條毛巾永遠都好臭，<br />\n係好刺鼻果種臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我嗰條毛巾同佢嗰條放係附近，好正常，無味。<br />\n我已經每個星期keep住幫佢換，但佢一用咗2,3日就已經開始發臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲知道點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想根治個問題</blockquote><br />\n識唔識用洗衣機傻女<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b33d40a79686bddd6599a51d5deb79194426896c","tid":178621,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:21:36.000Z","msg":"咁咪兩三日換一次<br />\n一星期換一次根本唔衛生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}